yromalabarqatar.org Syro Malabar Church in Qatar]\n*[http://www.syromalabarmatrimony.org/index.php Syro Malabar Matrimony]\n*[http://www.cnewa.org/default.aspx?ID=60&pagetypeID=9&sitecode=HQ&pageno=1 Article on the Syro-Malabar Catholic Church by Ronald Roberson on the CNEWA web site]\n*[http://www.fathimamathachurch.in/ Fathima Matha Church, East Hill , Kozhikode]\n\n{{Syro-Malabar Catholic Church Hierarchy}}\n{{Particular churches sui iuris footer}}\n{{Catholicism}}\n{{Christianity in Kerala}}\n{{Churches in India}}\n{{Syriac Christianity}}\n{{Christianity footer}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{coord|9.9823|N|76.2763|E|source:wikidata|display=title}}\n\n[[Category:1st-century establishments in India]]\n[[Category:Syro-Malabar Catholic Church| ]]\n", "text_old": "{{pp-protected|small=yes}}\n{{About|the Church based in India|the Church based in the Levant|Syriac Catholic Church}}\n{{Short description|Eastern Catholic Major Archiepiscopal Church}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=September 2019}}\n{{Infobox Christian denomination\n| name                = Syro-Malabar Catholic Church \n| native_name         =  {{lang-syc|\u0725\u0739\u0715\u072c\u0735\u0710 \u0715\u0721\u0732\u0720\u0732\u0712\u0735\u072a \u0723\u0718\u073c\u072a\u071d\u0735\u071d\u0735\u0710}}<br/>{{lang-mal|\u0d2e\u0d32\u0d2c\u0d3e\u0d31\u0d3f\u0d32\u0d46 \u0d38\u0d41\u0d31\u0d3f\u0d2f\u0d3e\u0d28\u0d3f \u0d15\u0d24\u0d4d\u0d24\u0d4b\u0d32\u0d3f\u0d15\u0d4d\u0d15 \u0d38\u0d2d}}\n| image               = Mar Thoma Sliva.jpg\n| caption             = The ''Mar Thoma Sliva'' or Saint Thomas Cross, the symbol of the Syro-Malabar Church\n| type                = [[Catholic particular churches and liturgical rites|Particular church]] (''[[sui iuris]]'')\n| main_classification = [[Eastern Catholic]]\n| orientation         = [[Syriac Christianity]]\n| scripture          = [[Peshitta]]<br>[[Bible translations into Malayalam#POC Bible|Malayalam POC Bible]]<ref>https://www.britannica.com/topic/Peshitta</ref>\n| polity        